phrases: But if that is the case, what would become of the Galactic Alliance
if the Hideauze are beaten completely?
What are you going to do, Ledo?
Chamber, do a search on work I could do here.
If there is work that you can do, there must be something for me...
It is irrelevant to compare yourself to this machine.
Non-battle duties that would be appropriate for you are close to nil.
In other words, I should just keep standing by, huh?
Agreement: It is early in the morning.
A component one of the hull interlocking devices.
They are really putting you to work, huh?
So that is actually a flute, right?
Even sound comes out... not useful.
You have spent all this time working on it...
For moving the cargo that last time.
Say, do not you have any money in space?
The Galactic Alliance does not allow personal possessions during military service.
That would put a damper on my motivation.
I want to... do my own work.
Yeah, that is not a bad idea!
What kind of work... there is?
It would be a pain if everyone had to hand-deliver letters and small packages, right?
So instead, I get paid for carrying them all around and delivering them.
That is how we support each other.
So first, you should think about what you want someone to do.
Well, maybe it will take a little time...
After all, you are still unfamiliar with the way we live.
Tell me... what I can do!
Um, would you happen to need a hand with your work?
He said he wants to do some kind of work.
So you are that Spaceboy everybody's talking about...
A worker here retired last month...
There is always enough room for one more fisherman.
This is how it is been recently, ever since we lost the rip current.
I will let you know when we get busy again.
As you can see, I am swamped trying to organize all of these invoices.
And it would be impossible for somebody with no experience to help.
We have a place in mind, but it will take another three days to get there.
I am sorry I got your hopes up.
Well, it is about time for me to do my deliveries...
Then I think I will search myself.
I did not think finding a job would be this difficult...
Chamber, have you updated your database?
As before, there are no jobs that match your aptitude.
The fleet's propulsion system is shutting down.
Do not stand there like a lump!
You need a change of pace!
It is a calm day is what is happening!
This is some huge meat, right?
It will go a long way!
I am impressed you got a hold of that.
But is it okay for you to party?
It is been so long since we have had a calm day and there is a lot of repair work that can be done...
My assistants are taking care of business while I am occupied with this.
We will start with Flange's ship.
Hey, you are supposed to do that work, Pinion!
The wind's stopped and there are no waves,
so we traditionally do ship maintenance on these calm days.
We take the fleet off of the Milky Way and turn off the power,
so everyone but repair technicians get to take a breather from work.
Not many know about this place.
Ledo, this is what the sea is like when there is no wind.
It sure is hot, is not it?
I will join you if you do not mind.
You do not know what I went through to get this fine meat.
Hey, cannot you get your tin can to do something about this?
There is something I want you to do.
I need you to fetch me something from that old bag of an ironsmith.
I mean, it is work that only you can do!
Hey, you are making Ledo go there?!
He ruined a whole plateful of meat, so yeah, of course!
I hope Ledo's going to be okay...
I am kind of ticklish there!
If I eat meat and stuff here, I will probably gain weight again...
You have got nothing to worry about!
Everybody's got their own norm, right?
I do not care about that.
A lot of boys prefer chubby girls.
Believe in a wrongheaded idea like that and you will end up getting hurt.
You know the crane tower sprinkler, right?
Even though the power's back on, it is not working.
Would you take the surf kite up to turn the pump on?
I have got a grill out party that is about to start...
I am not going to lose!
This way we do not have to worry about getting fat!
Query: Why are they so focused on maintaining their weight
even as they actively seek to eat in great quantities?
That is just the way girls think.
But I wonder how this will turn out.
Tin Can, I just noticed that you are black...
Oh, young man, are you alone?
You have got a sweet face...
The goal is the top of the crane tower!
What happened to fixing the winch on my boat?
I am still going to do it!
Is not now your busiest time?
Stick around and get some meat yourself.
We are going to be startin' in a little bit.
How about working at my place?!
The ensign is having an emergency.
I told you not to move!
He is just learning a thing or two about society.
What are you doing over here?
I was overseeing inspection and repairs of the bottom of the ship.
Hey, when is the power going to go back on in this area?
Work is taking longer than expected, so it will be off until this evening.
It is just, your swimsuit is pretty daring...
New workers do not have a quota or anything!
Looks like I am going to win this!
I am not going to lose!
You would have a good chance of being my club's number one!
Your bum has such a lovely shape!
You are dreamy... and have plenty of stamina, too!
Still, a race is a race!
Anyway, what were you doing there?
Well, I will go back to work.
The street you want is straight ahead!
Now we can eat a lot without worrying about it!
What do you intend to do with this?
Do I have to go back through there?
Dammit, who blabbed about the party?!
Seasoning with salt just are not enough.
You got back just in time!
That old lady's sauce is the best!
Ledo, if you do not get some now, it will be gone!
And try it with the fruit of your labors, too!
Well, better get back to work...
Did you get enough to eat?
Well, you did come in a bit late...
Even though the party was for you...
Pinion heard you could not find a job, so he planned the party to cheer you up.
Thanks for working hard for everyone is sake.
Thanks to that, we were all able to eat something delicious!
I will try to help you find work again!
I wonder what kind of work he would be suited for...
Probably some kind of physical labor?
So this is where you have been slacking off!
Wait, t-this is legitimate work here...
